        <description>An alien, corrupted metal aligned with Trell&#x27;s influence. It resists typical Investiture detection and interferes with other magic systems. Often associated with Hemalurgic constructs, Trellium&#x27;s strange red hue and unique properties hint at a Shardic power foreign to Scadrial.</description>

